   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_2_00015"/>Hrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich.
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb213" type="place">Ischl</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb41463" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Schulgasse 8</hi></rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_2_00013"/>Lieber Richard –</salute></opener><p>Ich verrei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e <date>Montag</date> oder <date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date>. Schreiben Sie mir vorher
               2 Zeilen. Ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en Sie vor der Waffenübg nach <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>? –</p><p>Haben Sie was über <pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_2_00014"/><rs ref="#pmb39775" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Freund</hi></rs> erfahren? –</p><p>– Ich treffe in <rs ref="#pmb897" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Lienz</hi></rs> oder<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o wo mit <rs ref="#pmb2167" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Salten</hi></rs> zusa<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en. –</p><p>Es ist unglaublich, dß Sie gar nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreiben.</p><closer>Herzlichen Gru<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s<lb/><signed><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_2_00014"/>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>18/8 93</date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
